_sText: This map is the similar idea of the following maps: surf fruits & surf vegestables. Hopefully you'll like this one as much as those. Remember guys these maps aren't suppose to be difficult they are suppose to be fun and easy to beat so everyone is able to get a chance in beating a surf map aswel. And for the "pro's" we have added a bonus level that is pretty hard. This map contains: - 1 Spawn - 10 Surf Stages - 1 Bonus Stage - 1 Jail - 1 Sliderace level You will be able to play the sliderace level whenever sombody beats the bonus level.
